{"word":"Wine","slug":"wine","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Wine</b> Made from grapes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=40&verse=11'>Gen 40:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=49&verse=11'>Gen 49:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=25&verse=6'>Isa 25:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=40&verse=10'>Jer 40:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=40&verse=12'>Jer 40:12</a><br/> Made from pomegranates<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=8&verse=2'>Son 8:2</a><br/> Kept in:<br/> - Jars<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=13&verse=12'>Jer 13:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=12'>Jer 48:12</a> <br/> - Skins<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=9&verse=4'>Jos 9:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=9&verse=13'>Jos 9:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=32&verse=19'>Job 32:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=9&verse=17'>Mat 9:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=38'>Luk 5:38</a> <br/> - Bottles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=9&verse=4'>Jos 9:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=9&verse=13'>Jos 9:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=32&verse=19'>Job 32:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=13&verse=12'>Jer 13:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=12'>Jer 48:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=9&verse=17'>Mat 9:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=38'>Luk 5:38</a> <br/> Cellars for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=27'>1Ch 27:27</a><br/> New wine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=37&chapter=1&verse=11'>Hag 1:11</a><br/> Old wine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=39'>Luk 5:39</a><br/> Medicinal use of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=31&verse=7'>Pro 31:7</a><br/> Medicinal use of, recommended by Paul to Timothy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=5&verse=23'>1Ti 5:23</a><br/> Used at meals<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=29'>Mat 26:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=23'>Mar 14:23</a><br/> Made by Jesus at the marriage feast in Cana<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=10'>Joh 2:10</a><br/> Sacramental use of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=29'>Mat 26:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=20'>Luk 22:20</a><br/> Forbidden to priests while on duty<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=9'>Lev 10:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=44&verse=21'>Eze 44:21</a><br/> Forbidden to Nazarites:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=6&verse=3'>Num 6:3</a><br/><a href='S:Nazarite'>Nazarite</a> <br/> Abstinence from:<br/> - Of Daniel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1&verse=5'>Dan 1:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1&verse=8'>Dan 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1&verse=16'>Dan 1:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=10&verse=3'>Dan 10:3</a> <br/> - Of courtiers of Ahasuerus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=1&verse=8'>Est 1:8</a> <br/> - Of Timothy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=5&verse=23'>1Ti 5:23</a> <br/> Samson's mother forbidden to drink<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=13&verse=5'>Jdg 13:5</a><br/> Forbidden to kings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=31&verse=4'>Pro 31:4</a><br/> Denied to the Israelites in the wilderness, that they might know that the Lord was their God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=29&verse=6'>Deu 29:6</a><br/> Offered with sacrifices<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=40'>Exo 29:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=13'>Lev 23:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=15&verse=5'>Num 15:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=15&verse=10'>Num 15:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=28&verse=7'>Num 28:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=28&verse=14'>Num 28:14</a><br/> Given by Melchizedek to Abraham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=18'>Gen 14:18</a><br/> Fermented<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=9'>Lev 10:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=6&verse=3'>Num 6:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=28&verse=7'>Num 28:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=14&verse=26'>Deu 14:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=29&verse=6'>Deu 29:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=23&verse=32'>Pro 23:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=2&verse=22'>Mar 2:22</a><br/> Refined<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=25&verse=6'>Isa 25:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=11'>Jer 48:11</a><br/> Of staggering<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=60&verse=3'>Psa 60:3</a><br/> Inflames the eyes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=49&verse=12'>Gen 49:12</a><br/> Commerce in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=18&verse=13'>Rev 18:13</a><br/> Banquets of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=5&verse=6'>Est 5:6</a><br/> Given to Jesus at the crucifixion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=48'>Mat 27:48</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=23'>Mar 15:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=36'>Luk 23:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=29'>Joh 19:29</a><br/> Intoxication from the use of wine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=104&verse=15'>Psa 104:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=4&verse=17'>Pro 4:17</a><br/> Instances of intoxication from:<br/> - Noah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=9&verse=21'>Gen 9:21</a> <br/> - Lot<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19&verse=32'>Gen 19:32</a> <br/> - Joseph and his brethren<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=43&verse=34'>Gen 43:34</a> <br/> - Nabal<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=25&verse=36'>1Sa 25:36</a> <br/> - Amnon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=29'>2Sa 13:29</a> <br/> - Ahasuerus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=1&verse=10'>Est 1:10</a> <br/> - Kings of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=7&verse=5'>Hos 7:5</a> <br/> - Falsely charged against the disciples<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=2&verse=13'>Act 2:13</a> <br/> Figurative:<br/> - Figurative:<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=60&verse=3'>Psa 60:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=